GeoMakers Scene Graph Generator Plug-ins
========================================

In this example there are two plug-ins being compiled into a single shared
object: SphereMaker generates several spheres in the scene and CubeMaker
generates cubes. The number of cubes/spheres can be controlled by the user.

Environment Variables
---------------------

KATANA_HOME  The Katana installation directory at compile-time

Building
--------

1. Ensure the environment variables listed above have been set.
2. Run 'make'.
3. Copy 'out/GeoMakers.so' to the 'Libs' subdirectory within a Katana
   resources path.
